    XIN CHO ANH/CH TI VI KHO HC BT NG SN VIT NAM 06/2019 [ PHN L THUYT ]

    1. BUI HC ONLINE U TIN CHNH THC BT U VO [ 9H SNG ] N [ 11H SNG ] TH BY NGY ( 15/06/2019 ) GI VIT NAM, KO DI T NHT 2 TING. BUI HC S C RECORD V UPLOAD LN GROUP HC VIN XEM LI.
    2. HC ONLINE QUA LINK ZOOM V LINK LIVE STREAM TRN KNH YOUTUBE CA HC VIN, CHNG TI S CP NHT 30 PHT LC [ 8H30 SNG ] TRC GI HC [ 9H SNG ].
    3. ANH/CH CN CHUN B SN IN THOI HO...C MY TNH C KT NI INTERNET, 1 TAI NGHE ( GIAO TIP R RNG)

    SAU BUI HC ONLINE, MI TUN GROUP S POST CC CLIP V CCH U T BDS BAO GM:

    1. Nguyn l BS.
    2. Php l BS chuyn su.
    3. Cc thut ng BS v xy dng c bn.

    SAU KHO HC BDSVN L THUYT, HC VIN S T TIN:

    - S dng ng cc thut ng thng dng trong BS.
    - c hiu ng: bn v xy dng, Giy chng nhn Quyn s dng t, Quyn s hu nh v ti sn khc gn lin vi t ("s hng"), vn bn php lut trong lnh vc BS.
    - T mnh thc hin c ton b cc th tc giao dch BS ng quy nh php lut hin hnh.

    CC CLIP MUA BN BDS THC T, PHN TCH TH TRNG CNG NH CHIN LC U T RING TNG BDS S C UPLOAD BN GROUP BDSVN THC T 06/2019
